---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — nosend.io"
  description="nosend.io privacy policy: we don't collect, store, or transmit your files. Zero tracking, zero analytics, no accounts, complete privacy."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="flex-1 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-600">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">The short version</h2>
        <p>We don't collect anything. Your files never leave your device. There are no accounts, no tracking, no analytics, and no servers involved in processing your files.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">How file processing works</h2>
        <p>All compression and conversion on nosend.io runs entirely inside your browser using standard web APIs. When you select a file, it is read locally by your browser and processed in memory. No file data is ever transmitted to any server.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Data we collect</h2>
        <p>None. We do not collect personal information, usage data, or file metadata. We do not use cookies or local storage for tracking purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Third-party services</h2>
        <p>nosend.io is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect standard web server logs (IP address, request path, timestamp) as part of serving the site. This is outside our control.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Cloudflare also provides Real User Monitoring (RUM) on this site. RUM collects anonymous performance data, such as page load times and connection quality, to help us understand how the site performs for real visitors and identify areas for improvement. No personal information or file data is collected through RUM. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-indigo-600 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a> for details.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Donations</h2>
        <p>If you choose to donate via Ko-fi or cryptocurrency, those transactions are handled entirely by those platforms. We do not receive or store any payment details.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>If we ever change how this site works in a way that affects privacy, we will update this page. The date at the top reflects when this policy was last revised.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
